<font face="Times New Roman, Times, serif" size="5"><b>On the picket line</b></font></P>
<p><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">December 7, 2001 | Page 11</font></p>

<p><font face="Times New Roman, Times, serif" size="3">OTHER STORIES BELOW<br>
<a href="#Airlines">United Airlines</a><br>
<a href="#convention">AFL-CIO convention</a><br>
<a href="#Supremo">V&amp;V Supremo Foods</a><br>
